Festival of Mountain Music and Dance. Concert performance at the ruins of the Grand Hotel (Casa Grande) in Managua, Nicaragua. Susie Goff and the Green Grass Cloggers, Mick Moloney (mandolin) and Robbie O'Connell (guitar, vocals) perform as part of the South American tour of Irish and Appalachian musicians for the United States Information Agency.
